data.description: ***Seller is offering $4,000 towards buyer's closing costs*** Step into the enchanting ambiance of 313 E Platt St., a delightful Long Beach home built in 1990. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence seamlessly blends comfort and style, with a spacious living room featuring a cozy fireplace at its heart. The outdoor patio serves as a relaxing oasis, complete with a jacuzzi, waterfall, and inviting lights. The well-equipped kitchen, with modern appliances and a built-in bar, is perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom offers a tranquil retreat with a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a unique Victorian claw-footed bathtub and direct access to the serene patio. Ample closet space in all bedrooms ensures a clutter-free environment, and the convenience of a two-car garage plus additional parking adds to the home's appeal. Located in a lively Long Beach neighborhood, this home combines 1990s charm with contemporary living, ready to create lasting memories. Act quickly before it's too late!
